<plot>We interview co-producer and star Jennifer Lopez along with her long time friend and collaborator, director Gregory Nava, co-stars Martin Sheen and Maya Zapata about the filming of this important, contemporary story based on the facts of the Juarez murders. Lopez accepts an "Artists for Amnesty" award from the human rights organization Amnesty International in the documentary.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?185867</url></doc>
